<template>
  <el-steps :active="2">
    <el-step title="简历审核" description=""></el-step>
    <el-step title="基础信息咨询" description=""></el-step>
    <el-step title="面试" description=""></el-step>
    <el-step title="就业协议书" description=""></el-step>
    <el-step title="招聘完成" description=""></el-step>
  </el-steps>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  mounted() {
    if(this.$route.query.rpId == undefined) {
      const loading = this.$loading({
        lock: true,
        text: 'Loading',
        spinner: 'el-icon-loading',
        background: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)'
      });
      setTimeout(() => {
        loading.close();
      }, 2000);
      this.$router.push('/GraduateEmploymentNeed');
      this.$notify({
        title: '提示',
        message: '请选择某一招聘过程',
        iconClass: 'el-icon-mouse'
      })
    }
  },

  data() {
    return {
      tableData: [
        {
          enId: '1',
          graduateId: '6',
          rpPhase: '简历审核'
        }]
    }
  },

  methods: {
    goto(row) {
      this.$router.push({
        path: '/GraduateRecruitmentProcess',
        query: {
          id:1
        }
      })
    }
  }
}
</script>
